<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT24">
<l>nikaḻntāypāṟ poṉpacuppuk kārvaṇṇa nāṉku</l>
<l>mikaḻntā yiruvaraiyum vīyap pukaḻntāy</l>
<l>ciṉappōrc cuvētaṉaic cēṉā patiyāy</l>
<l>maṉappōr muṭikkum vakai</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You shone in all four hues, white, [red] gold, green, [and] black;</l>
<l>You despised [Madhu and Kaiṭabha] so that both perished;</l>
<l>Becoming the commander of the [Pāṇḍava] army, [You] praised the angry, belligerent</l>
<l rend="indent">Man with white horses [Arjuna]</l>
<l>[in such a] way that [he] ended the war [as per Your] heart’s [wish].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
